(6, 1, '2017-08-29 06:55:00', '2017-08-29 06:55:00', '[vc_row el_class=\"text-dark first-home\"][vc_column el_class=\"content banner\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"first-banner\"]\r\n<h1>Myanmar Accounting Tax Auditing</h1>\r\nGlobal Think Accounting Co., Ltd. (GTA) is an accounting firm established in Myanmar by a Japanese certified public accountant on 6 July, 2015.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_wp_custommenu nav_menu=\"21\" el_class=\"first-menu content\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1611560932856{padding-top: 90px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"home-sec sec\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-sec-tp\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content lf\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"907\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" el_class=\"content lf\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content rg\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>WHO ARE WE</h4>\r\n<h3>What should We do to make each Myanmar employee shine and work?</h3>\r\nWe have been searching for an answer to this question for a long time. In order to deliver high quality accounting services, it is essential to develop our staff at a detailed level in all areas. We place a lot of importance on internal training, but we also place a lot of importance on overcoming difficult tasks. We need to continue to grow ourselves while providing valuable services to our clients. We believe that by continuing to focus on the people in front of us with sincerity, we will continue to be needed by those around us and each of our staff will continue to shine.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/global-think/who-are-we/\">READ MORE</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-sec-bt\"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text][our_home_portfolio][/our_home_portfolio][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-sec-goal\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content goal-cnt\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>What is the goal of our group?</h3>\r\nOur business objective is to continue to provide accounting, tax and auditing services that earn the trust of our clients. We assure you that the financial statements we provide are reliable. We will continue to provide global quality services from Myanmar.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/global-think/our-services/\">READ MORE</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1610702442905{padding-bottom: 90px !important;}\" el_class=\"home-third sec\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-th-tp\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"908\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content rg advanced\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Myanmar\r\nAdvance Guide for you</h3>\r\nAre you thinking of expanding your business in Myanmar?\r\nGet the latest Myanmar information.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/global-think/our_news/regarding-our-view-on-changes-in-the-accounting-period/\">READ MORE</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-th-bt\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content news-hd\" width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>NEWS</h4>\r\n<h3>Pick up</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content home-news\" width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text][our_home_news_content][/our_home_news_content][/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class=\"content rg\"><a href=\"/global-think/infomation/\">Read More</a></div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2021-01-28 08:31:44', '2021-01-28 08:31:44', '', 0, 'http://demo.archiwp.com/fresh-version/?page_id=6', 0, 'page', '', 0),
