(1073, 1, '2021-01-25 07:49:06', '2021-01-25 07:49:06', '[vc_row el_class=\"text-dark first-home\"][vc_column el_class=\"content banner\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"first-banner\"]\r\n<h1>Myanmar Accounting Tax Consulting</h1>\r\nGlobal Think Accounting Co., Ltd. (GTA) is an accounting firm established in Myanmar by a Japanese certified public accountant on July 6, 2015.[/vc_column_text][vc_wp_custommenu nav_menu=\"21\" el_class=\"first-menu content\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1611560932856{padding-top: 90px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"home-sec sec\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-sec-tp\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content lf\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"907\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" el_class=\"content lf\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content rg\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>WHO ARE WE</h4>\r\n<h3>What should I do to make each Myanmar employee shine and work?</h3>\r\nWhat we have cherished is the thorough education of our employees. I’ve been searching for answers about the theme, “What should I do to make each Myanmar employee shine and work?” In order to deliver high-quality services, the growth of employees is indispensable, so we have cherished overcoming difficult tasks. Things that are common and easy in Japan are not common and easy in Myanmar.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"#\">READ MORE</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-sec-bt\"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text][our_home_portfolio][/our_home_portfolio][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-sec-goal\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content goal-cnt\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>What is the goal of our company?</h3>\r\nThere is no final destination in our business, but our goal is to continue providing services that our customers trust. We must continue to grow while providing valuable services to our business partners. By earnestly helping the people in front of us, we believe that we will continue to be needed by the people around us, and each employee’s life will continue to shine.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"#\">READ MORE</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1610702442905{padding-bottom: 90px !important;}\" el_class=\"home-third sec\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-th-tp\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"908\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content rg advanced\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Myanmar\r\nAdvance Guide for you</h3>\r\nAre you thinking of expanding your business in Myanmar?\r\nGet the latest Myanmar information.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"#\">READ MORE</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\"home-th-bt\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content news-hd\" width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>NEWS</h4>\r\n<h3>Pick up</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"content home-news\" width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text][our_home_news_content][/our_home_news_content][/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class=\"content rg\"><a href=\"#\">Read More</a></div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-25 07:49:06', '2021-01-25 07:49:06', '', 6, 'http://web-dev.88175848-86-20200805092356.webstarterz.com/global-think/2021/01/25/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
