(1106, 1, '2021-01-26 04:52:35', '2021-01-26 04:52:35', '[vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" el_class=\"first-way way\"][vc_column el_class=\"content frt\"][vc_column_text]Our business objective is to continue to provide accounting, tax and auditing services that earn the trust of our clients. We assure you that the financial statements we provide are reliable. We will continue to provide global quality services from Myanmar.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" el_class=\"way sec-way\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"841\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" el_class=\"content sec\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" el_class=\"way third-way\"][vc_column el_class=\"content third\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>What do we need to do to help each and every Myanmar staff member shine in work?</h3>\r\nWe have been searching for an answer to this question for a long time. In order to deliver high quality accounting services, it is essential to develop our staff at a detailed level in all areas. We place a lot of importance on internal training, but we also place a lot of importance on overcoming difficult tasks. We need to continue to grow ourselves while providing valuable services to our clients. We believe that by continuing to focus on the people in front of us with sincerity, we will continue to be needed by those around us and each of our staff will continue to shine.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_section el_class=\"forth-way way\"][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" el_class=\"sec\"][vc_column el_class=\"content fourth\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Member</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" el_class=\"third\"][vc_column el_class=\"content member-post\"][vc_column_text][our_home_member][/our_home_member][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row fullwidth=\"yes\" el_class=\"fifth-way way\"][vc_column el_class=\"content fifth\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Compan